{"id":76965,"title":"Patient and family views of nutritional status.","abstract":"Providing adequate food in hospitals remains a concern for those involved in healthcare as well as patients and relatives. We conducted a small-scale survey to explore relatives' and patients' perceptions about the risk of developing malnutrition in hospital and to gauge whether further more in-depth audit was required.","date":"2014-05-30","categories":"Nutritional and Metabolic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24873106","annotations":[{"name":"Nutrition","weight":0.747438,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nutrition"},{"name":"Food","weight":0.644842,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Food"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.6439,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.403857,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.355874,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Perception","weight":0.20687,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perception"},{"name":"Audit","weight":0.14573,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Audit"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.0551856,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Statistical survey","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_survey"},{"name":"Family (biology)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Family_(biology)"},{"name":"Track gauge","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Track_gauge"},{"name":"Malnutrition","weight":0.0154274,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malnutrition"}]}
